Title of the Epic: Forum Feature Enhancements
Description: Enhance the features and functionality of the web development community forum to improve user engagement and satisfaction.

Goals:

Improve user experience on the forum
Increase user engagement and participation
Increase user satisfaction with the forum
User Stories:

As a forum user, I want to be able to easily search for topics of interest so that I can find relevant information quickly.
As a forum user, I want to be able to save my favorite topics for quick access later.
As a forum user, I want to be able to receive notifications when new posts are made to topics I'm interested in.
Dependencies: None

Risks:

The new features may not be well-received by forum users.
The new features may be difficult to implement and cause delays.
Estimated Effort: 3-4 sprints

Business Value: Improved user engagement, satisfaction, and retention.

Priority: High
